'''里斯·布朗'''（{{lang-en|'''Reece Brown'''}}；{{bd|1996年|3月3日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，在場上的位置是中場。現時被[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲尔德]]外借至[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]球隊[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼得伯勒联]]。

==球會生涯==
布朗10歲時便加入[[伯明翰城足球俱樂部|伯明翰城]]青年學院<ref name=BlueKid>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20130731-blue-kid-on-the-block-reece-brown-957773.aspx |title=Blue kid on the block – Reece Brown |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=31 July 2013 |accessdate=1 August 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130803171818/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20130731-blue-kid-on-the-block-reece-brown-957773.aspx |archivedate=2013年8月3日 }}</ref>，2012年7月獲得獎學金，在球會的U18展開其足球事業<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/~/media/Files/TheFAPortal/governance-docs/registrations/july-2012.ashx |title=List of Players Registered as Scholars in Accordance with Rule C.3 Between 01/07/2012 and 31/07/2012 |publisher=The Football Association |accessdate=6 August 2013 |archive-date=2016-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203215924/http://www.thefa.com/~/media/Files/TheFAPortal/governance-docs/registrations/july-2012.ashx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年9月17日，他首次在職業聯賽上場，在以3-0不敵[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|伯恩利]]賽事中入替[[达伦·安布罗斯|达伦·安布罗斯]]上場<ref name=Debut>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24028130 |title=Burnley 3–0 Birmingham |publisher=BBC Sport |date=17 September 2013 |accessdate=17 September 2013 |archive-date=2014-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412021937/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24028130 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年1月18日主場對[[约维尔足球俱乐部|约维尔]]的比賽，他首次先發上場並當選為伯明翰全場最佳球員<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/birmingham-city-0-yeovil-town-6528349 |title=Birmingham City 0 Yeovil Town 2 |author=Tattum, Colin |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=20 January 2014 |accessdate=21 January 2014 |archive-date=2021-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323121309/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/birmingham-city-0-yeovil-town-6528349 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後他與球會簽下職業合約至2016年<ref name=TurnsPro>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140124-reece-brown-pens-pro-deal-1314553.aspx |title=Reece Brown pens pro deal |author=Walker, Andy |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=24 January 2014 |accessdate=24 January 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140129095000/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140124-reece-brown-pens-pro-deal-1314553.aspx |archivedate=2014-01-29}}</ref>。

===諾士郡===
2014/15球季，在首6場賽事只獲得1次上場機會的他被外借到[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]一個月<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140828-official-reece-brown-joins-notts-county-1880797.aspx |title=Official: Reece Brown joins Notts County |publisher=Birmingham City F.C |date=28 August 2014 |accessdate=28 August 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828155715/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140828-official-reece-brown-joins-notts-county-1880797.aspx |archivedate=2014年8月28日 }}</ref>。在新球會首場比賽對[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔城]]便先發上場踢了64分鐘<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28917045 |title=Notts County 1–2 Bristol City |publisher=BBC Sport |date=31 August 2014 |accessdate=3 September 2014 |archive-date=2014-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014054516/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28917045 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。外借到期共上場4次，之後因傷提前終止租約<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nottinghampost.com/Notts-County-Winger-Reece-Brown-returns/story-22987477-detail/story.html |title=Notts County: Winger Reece Brown returns to Birmingham City |newspaper=Nottingham Post |date=25 September 2014 |accessdate=29 September 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
2011年11月25日，布朗首次替[[英格蘭16歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U16]]上場，在{{le|勝利盾|Victory Shield}}對{{le|蘇格蘭U16|Scotland_national_under-16_football_team}}的比賽在半場換入<ref name=FAprofile>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/All-Teams/Players/B/reece-brown-96 |title=Reece Brown (1996) |publisher=The Football Association |accessdate=6 August 2013 |archive-date=2013-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227075018/http://www.thefa.com/england/all-teams/players/b/reece-brown-96 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u16s/News/match-centre/2011/ScotlandvEngland |title=Victory Shield clinched in style |author=Marshall, James |publisher=The Football Association |date=25 November 2011 |accessdate=6 August 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20120428064846/http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u16s/News/match-centre/2011/ScotlandvEngland |archivedate=2012年4月28日 }}</ref>。2012年{{le|蒙太古国际足球邀请赛|Montaigu Tournament}}他代表U16參賽3次，而英格蘭在半決賽的[[點球大戰|點球大戰]]中不敵俄羅斯U16<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u16s/News/match-centre/2012/japanvengland |title=Late show for young Lions |publisher=The Football Association |date=3 April 2012 |accessdate=6 August 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023224643/http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u16s/News/match-centre/2012/japanvengland |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u16s/News/match-centre/2012/englandvrussia |title=Shootout heartbreak for young Lions |publisher=The Football Association |date=7 April 2012 |accessdate=6 August 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023232213/http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u16s/News/match-centre/2012/englandvrussia |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但成功擊敗法國取得第三名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u16s/News/match-centre/2012/france-england-montaigu |title=Lions finish third in Montaigu |publisher=The Football Association |date=9 April 2012 |accessdate=6 August 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023213207/http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u16s/News/match-centre/2012/france-england-montaigu |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年8月31日，布朗在U17處子戰便取得入球以4-1擊敗{{le|土耳其U17|Turkey_national_under-17_football_team}}<ref name=BlueKid/>。{{le|2013年歐洲U-17足球錦標賽|2013 UEFA European Under-17 Championship}}資格賽中，布朗所上場3次的比賽皆取得勝利<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uefa.com/under17/season=2013/teams/player=250056556/index.html |title=Under-17 – Reece Brown |publisher=UEFA |date=15 November 2012 |accessdate=6 August 2013 |archive-date=2012-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028231106/http://www.uefa.com/under17/season=2013/teams/player=250056556/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年11月，他被U18徵召參加集訓營<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u18s/News/2013/training-camp-squad-051113 |title=Training days |publisher=The Football Association |date=5 November 2013 |accessdate=6 November 2013 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630195710/http://www.thefa.com/england/mens-u18s/News/2013/training-camp-squad-051113 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在2014年3月3日首次替U18上場<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2014/mar/england-under-18-2-1-croatia |title=England Under-18s rattled by Croatia comeback |first=Nicholas |last=Veevers |publisher=The Football Association |date=3 March 2014 |accessdate=3 March 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630195716/http://www.thefa.com/news/2014/mar/03/england-under-18-2-1-croatia |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

